1.1.name: wordpress/financial-mathematics
1.1.description: This plugin provides a shortcode which render forms that calculate and explain annuities certain, repayment mortgages etc: maths questions which typically appear in the CT1 actuarial exam and the Interest Theory part of the Financial Mathematics exam.
